title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.03.08
description:
WHO GIVES YOU THE RIGHT?:
    -------------------------
    When jealousy goes too far... Heidi&#039;s been consistently abused by husband Octavio for too long, and she&#039;s finally ready to put a stop to it. Things have gotten so bad, Octavio locks Heidi in her own room, holding her hostage against her will, because he suspects her of cheating. Heidi&#039;s reached out to Steve to help her confront Octavio and regain her sense of freedom, and safety. Can Steve help end this abuser&#039;s attacks, or will Heidi remain helpless? 

ENJOY PLEASE SEED AND SAY THANK YOU
